HEADWORD: After damp
<hw>Aft"er damp`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.<def>An irrespirable gas, remaining
after an explosion of fire damp in mines; choke damp. See <er>Carbonic
acid</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
